            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:89a571a4-c109-494e-b78d-a00700a270f3</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/bearings/~3/S2oA8nd_j8c/kittiwake-bearing-checker</link>
