            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:04ce1f57-520e-4da4-a8ca-9f510111507d</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/bearings/~3/4XOjCKOc7eA/royal-bearing-acquires-inventory</link>
