            <title>A joint journey toward world-class maintenance</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	SAPA Heat Transfer, Sweden, has worked closely with SKF for a number of years and managed to reduce its maintenance costs and increase uptime in production.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/bearings/~4/8KFQ4jX-2Kg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
