            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:2a6cc5be-4de3-4c1f-a117-9d3b009c5dde</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/bearings/~3/u777oe3Pbxw/consistency-ash-grove-reliability</link>
