            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:abf42b8f-1f68-4693-98c8-9cf800da24a4</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/bearings/~3/Fj11GgXkAzc/new-bearings-extend-life-on-hardwood-mill's-induced-draft-fan-</link>
