            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:c2e4aada-d232-4169-a99f-9cf800e312c9</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/bearings/~3/ThdP2074Hog/timken-seeks-energy-efficiency-in-bearing-applications</link>
