&lt;P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"&gt;&lt;SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: Arial"&gt;The Bearing Handbook is available from Applied for no charge at &lt;A title=http://www.applied.com/bearinghandbook href="http://www.applied.com/bearinghandbook"&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;FONT color=#0000ff&gt;www.Applied.com/bearinghandbook&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;
